    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no chips, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that remains supple and all technology features functioning perfectly. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and represents the highest standard of care, making it a perfect find for a collector or discerning buyer who demands the very best.",
