    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle is preserved in showroom condition, exhibiting impeccable aesthetic and mechanical integrity. Meticulously maintained and free of any discernible wear, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning motorist who demands nothing short of perfection. Experience the pinnacle of pre-owned luxury in a vehicle that presents as entirely new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
